collectible.name: MAD MADE APE VOXEL #01
collectible.author: 0x5f4758636a13380372eea46a5cf15a0e7e470a61
collectible.description: He looks like me, he said. It's not my fault that my creation happens to look like a real being from the future, was my reply. It is a Mad Made Ape he said and explained after humans were mysteriously gone the things we minted still do their task in the metaverse. All our characters will have survived and a glitch later a solar powered mega 3d print plant starts to produce the art we sculpted. Some God Acid and the nature of the evolutionary universe transformed all figures in actual living beings. Imagine that. I listen to him an finally agreed, Ok you know what it looks not like you but one of you!
